target: player
agent_profile: null
validations:
  - name: player_mechanics
    type: agent_validation
    severity: error
    args:
      rubric: >
        Verify the player implementation includes:
        1. A five-pointed star rendered with Canvas 2D path drawing.
        2. Horizontal movement with acceleration/deceleration (not instant).
        3. Variable-height jumping (hold for higher, release to cut short).
        4. A spin/dash attack with a cooldown that interacts differently with triangle, square, and circle enemies.
        5. Health system with 3 HP per life and 3 lives total.
        6. Invincibility frames after taking damage with a visual flash effect.
        7. Instant death on falling off-screen, with respawn at level start or checkpoint.
